    "title": "Lead SEO Specialist at Zepto South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Are you a skilled SEO Specialist looking for your next big career move? Zepto South Asia Partners in Varanasi offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Zepto South Asia Partners:\nZepto South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zepto South Asia Partners!",
